OL,3,CNature 'emergency' declared as annual
OL,4,Cbutterfly survey shows record lows
OL,6,FConservations have called on the
OL,7,Fgovernment to declare a "nature
OL,8,Femergency" after this year's Big
OL,9,FButterfly Count recorded its worst
OL,10,Fever results.
OL,12,FThe numbers were the lowest in the
OL,13,Fcount's 14-year history, with
OL,14,Fparticipants spotting just seven
OL,15,Fbutterflies on average per count, down
OL,16,Falmost half on last year's average of
OL,17,F12, and the lowest the survey has seen.
