OL,4,Cbutterfly survey shows record lows
OL,6,FEach year wildlife charity Butterfly
OL,7,FConservation asks people across the UK
OL,8,Fto spend 15 minutes recording the
OL,9,Fbutterflies they see in their gardens,
OL,10,Fparks or local countryside.
OL,12,FThis year, many species, including
OL,13,Fincluding the Common Blue, Small
OL,14,FTortoiseshell, Painted Lady and Scotch
OL,15,FArgus, showed a steep decline numbers
OL,16,Fcompared to 2023.
