OL,6,FHe blamed intensive management of the
OL,7,Fcountryside and gardens, including
OL,8,Ffrom an "obsession with tidiness
OL,9,Fthat's just really bad for nature".
OL,11,FButterfly Conservation is now writing
OL,12,Fan open letter to Environment
OL,13,FSecretary Steve Reed, calling on the
OL,14,Fgovernment to declare a "nature
OL,15,Femergency" and further restrictions on
OL,16,Fcertain pesticides, known as
OL,17,Fneonicotinoids.
