OL,4,Cbutterfly survey shows record lows
OL,6,F"When used on farmland, these
OL,7,Fchemicals make their way into the wild
OL,8,Fplants growing at field edges,
OL,9,Fresulting in adult butterflies and
OL,10,Fmoths drinking contaminated nectar and
OL,11,Fcaterpillars feeding on contaminated
OL,12,Fplants," Dr Fox said.
OL,14,F"If we don't act now to address the
OL,15,Flong-term drivers of butterfly
OL,16,Fdecline, we will face extinction
OL,17,Fevents never before seen in our
OL,18,Flifetime."
