OL,6,FHe said the neonicotinoid ban on its
OL,7,Fown would not reverse the declines,
OL,8,Fbut would have a positive impact on
OL,9,Finsects.
OL,11,FButterflies are a key indicator
OL,12,Fspecies; when they are in trouble we
OL,13,Fknow that the wider environment is in
OL,14,Ftrouble too.
OL,16,FIn total, just over 935,000
OL,17,Fbutterflies and day-flying moths were
OL,18,Frecorded across the UK, in the period
OL,19,Ffrom July 12 to August 4, down more
OL,20,Fthan a third on 2023's figures.
